Dialogs.Dialog: 高嶺
Do you remember the song "Hato Poppo"?
Oh, I sang it when I was in kindergarten.
The part of the song that says "If you want it", sounds a little arrogant. I feel like looking down on someone.
...Are you looking down on a pigeon?
How would you feel if you were a pigeon? Try to feel like a pigeon.
Feeling like a pigeon, huh... Po... Popopo.
That's just the sound it makes. It's not like that, just try to imagine you're a pigeon.
The feeling of a pigeon feeling... I'll think about it.
It's about our talk about pigeons from last time.
高嶺
Ah, yes. Did you think about it?
I think it's a problem that involves pigeons, too. They act like "I'm going to whatever", and then they eat.
You mean pigeons are bad?
I was thinking that maybe the pigeons need to change their mindset.
Something like a change of heart for the pigeons?
Like, "you can't eat if you act mighty while flying". I think that kind of attitude is...
But I think if I have something I like in front of me, I will eat it based on my instincts.
If you have something you like in front of you...
What's wrong? Saying that so suddenly...
高嶺
I was thinking about the song "Hato Poppo", but...
Ah, did you come up with a way to make pigeons change their minds?
Why don't we change the lyrics instead?
Huh, what do you mean?
Something like "How are you? If you want beans, I'll give you♪"
... Hey, I think it's not bad. However, I feel it still doesn't solve the problem.
What do you think if we change the way they see the world? And we change the composition along the way.
You're right, it may be good to change "I'll give you" to "Can you eat with me?"...
Are you going to eat with the pigeons?
Yes, of course. Not only with pigeons, but also human beings will change their consciousness.
Fufu, will we do it too?
高嶺
I give the song "Hato Poppo" a thought.
I'm still thinking about it.
I don't think it's because we need to scare pigeon-san away.
"Pigeon-san"?
Yes. So I was thinking about new making lyrics...
Well, I thought about it the other day, but I can't change old masterpieces without permission.
But, think about the feelings of the pigeons... Speaking of which, what do you think about their feelings?
For that... I'm going to ask the pigeon directly.
Can you understand what they say?
I'll listen to them when we go to the park on a date. If there's a pigeon there then...
Fufu, really?
高嶺
...Hey, what do you do when you can't sleep at night?
I think about you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Take it seriously!
I'm serious, really. I think about you ▲高嶺＊＊▲, and then I can fall asleep.
With me? Can you sleep when you think about me?
Something like that. I don't know what to say, but your memory makes me so happy and mentally calm.
I'm not sure, but if you think about me, and you can sleep. Do you think it'll work for Ako-chan?
Ako-chan?
My cousin. She asked me about what to do with her lack of sleep. Then I'll... I'll tell her that she must think of me.
Wait, wait a second. Don't do that!
Why?
高嶺
Ako-chan still can't sleep well...
That was your cousin, right?
Right. We live a bit apart but we're near the same age.
Huh, I'm sure your cousin is a beautiful woman, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I think she's much more beautiful than me.
That's not true.
...You've never met Ako-chan, right? I don't think you know her face or her style.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, there's no way she's more beautiful than you.
...Yes, she is. There are a lot of girls a lot more beautiful than me.
Not here. At least not in my world.
...That must be a strange world.
高嶺
Ako-chan asked for my help again...
You cousin with insomnia?
It's not insomnia, it's just that she can't sleep that easy... Do you know of something?
Why doesn't she go to the batting center before going to bed and do some exercise?
She's a girl, so that kind of thing...
Counting up to 50,000 sheep?
I think she has counted enough sheep already...
Having something to eat before sleeping? She might relax her body and mind.
But eating before going to bed is not good for you.
It's just a light meal... I don't know what else to do.
Hmm...
高嶺
Ako-chan said she could sleep with a lettuce.
Oh, I'm glad to hear it. What, lettuce? Can you sleep after eating it? or did you create it ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Not me, I remembered seeing it in the British rabbit picture book, and it said lettuce could help.
...I don't really understand what you're talking about.
In the picture book, the rabbits always fell asleep after eating lettuce. I remembered that part.
...Is Ako-chan a rabbit?
Fufu, she's human. But maybe I'm the one who's actually a rabbit. When I tried to eat it, I became sleepy...
Really? I wonder if it would work for me. There are times when I can't sleep.
Maybe you should try after some time. And, you're not a little rabbit. A capybara, maybe?
Me? A capybara? Why such a maniac animal... Do I look like that?
Ufufu, why are you making that face? Thank you for taking the hint.
高嶺
What kind of pet would you like to keep?
I can't keep pets in my room...
Then, what if you could keep one?
...Honestly, it would be a goldfish or a turtle. They don't take up that much space and are easy to take care.
For turtles, rabbits are a better company.
"The Rabbit and the turtle". That doesn't sound like a good combination.
Then just a rabbit! If you want to keep one, rabbits are the best choice, right?
You're talking about "ifs", aren't you?
高嶺
Hey, if you could keep a rabbit, what kind of breed would you like?
Breeds... Are there that many kinds of rabbits?
The Netherlands Dwarf, Lop ear, Angola...
...The normal one it's fine. The white one that usually appears in fairy tales.
Japanese White.
That's the one, white rabbits are cute.
Say it again.
I don't mind, but why do you want to hear about fairy tales?
Not that one, the other one.
"White rabbits are cute".
Fufu♪ Right?
Huh?
高嶺
Hey, if you could keep a rabbit...
I know the topic comes often, but I can't keep pets in my room.
It may be someday when you can keep one. It doesn't have to be immediately.
Someday...
Won't you like to have pets around the house?
It's not that I don't like them, but the room must be larger.
That'll be fine.
I'm not there during the day, so I won't be able to feed them.
It's okay, I'll be waiting for you to come back.
You're very confident about this.
I'm a rabbit, so it's okay.
As we were saying before, keeping a dog as a pet is not an option either.
高嶺
That's no good.
... A cat?
I said a rabbit. I won't listen to any more suggestions.
Well, a rabbit might be okay...
If we'll live together, it has to be a rabbit.
You really like rabbits. But to keep one for myself is just a tall order.
That's not related to this.
Huh? What do you mean?
I'm talking about who will live with you.
With me? But I live alone.
Right now, right? I'm talking about having a family in the future.
高嶺
An emergency patient arrived to my house the other day...
Huh? Is your house an emergency designated hospital, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
It's not, but it'll be rude to send away the people. He was an ojisan who was brought to my family.
Why didn't you call for an ambulance?
He said he doesn't like ambulances. Because he thinks he's bothering other people.
But then it might be more annoying to have him in your house, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It's an important patient, so it's natural for Papa to receive them.
Yeah, that's fine. So, what about the old man?
We went to the emergency center by ambulance. He had something dangerous, but after being received, he was safe.
So he got into an ambulance after all. If he's fine, then it was worth it.
高嶺
The ojisan who was sick last time was admitted at the university hospital.
I thought he didn't like ambulances.
I was hard to persuade him to get on.
I see, he was stubborn.
And after that, I got a phone call from the hospital to thank me...
I see, he was fine enough to call you.
I wonder if he used the hospital phone. Papa said he couldn't walk because of his symptoms.
I don't think that could stop him, a stubborn person has a strong sense of duty.
I just hope that doesn't make his symptoms worse...
There are a lot of people who can use their phones in the hospital now, maybe he went stayed in bed after all?
Do you think the ojisan can use a cell phone...
（That's right, some people have difficulties adjusting to technology... Like ▲高嶺＊＊▲）
高嶺
The ojisan called in to thank me.
Ah, is he still in the hospital?
He can barely walk now, so he'll be leaving the hospital soon.
I see. Why doesn't he stay?
Because Papa doesn't receive any payment, except medical treatment fees.
I see your father is not stubborn ▲高嶺＊＊▲... He's a straight person.
Fufu, he is stubborn, indeed.
I see... I think it'll be a lot of trouble if the father of my girlfriend is stubborn.
Really? Why?
Like when I say "Give me your daughter's hand please" he will say "I'm not going to do it".
... Oh you.
高嶺
The ojisan told me he will be leaving the hospital soon.
I see, make sure he doesn't forget to bring a thank-you gift to your house ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I'm sure Papa won't take it.
Hmm, but why? I don't understand.
It would be rude to return an item you received as a thank-you.
If you park an ambulance in front of your house, the ojisan won't get in.
Ambulances can't be used for that purpose.
Then ask your father to dress as an ambulance.
It's impossible... Fufu, Papa as an ambulance?
Yes. You know, with cardboard or something.
Fufu, fufufu. I'm sorry, Papa... That was so funny.
高嶺
Did you know there is a tale about a King with the donkey ears.
Yeah, I've heard about it.
Huh, I wonder who you can find you're a donkey with just your ears.
...Yes, with just the ears it's hard to tell whether it's a donkey, a horse or a dog.
If you have pig's ears, you can be find easily.
I'm sorry, but having pig's ears would make me be eaten. I'm sure it would be a strange tale.
Do you eat pig's ears?
Mimigar is an Okinawan food made from pig's ears. I've eaten it before.
So you ate them... But we weren't talking about Okinawa, were we?
I mean, that's a place were you don't see donkey ears as edible. Do you know were we can find a place like that?
I think every country must be the same... I'm sure.
We were talking about the King with donkey ears, right? It would be easy to understand if it was a rabbit.
高嶺
Yeah, if it jumps around it can't hide it's ears.
I think it would be popular. The Bunny King! After all, there's a bunny girl next to me.
...What's wrong? You're staring at me.
I think the rabbit ears would look good on you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Me... a bunny girl next to the king?
I'm sure it would look good on you. Yes, I really think so.
I don't want that... But, I might be consider it if you are the king.
（I think being King would be hard）
高嶺
Hey, you work part-time, correct?
Hmm? Yeah, I do.
I want to try too. I think I'll give it a try.
Why? Don't you have enough pocket money.
No, that's not why... For my social studies, I guess?
Ah, I see.
And for you...
Me?
I want to learn from you, be it at school, club activities or part-time jobs.
（She's serious about wanting learn from me...）
By the way, what happened to your wish of having a part-time job?
高嶺
Ah, for that... I spoke with Mama and Papa...
Oh, and did they told you?
Papa said "High school students should only focus on their studies and club activities".
I see... But that's fine, isn't it?
Why?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, if you work part-time we would spend less time together.
I see, but...
No buts, in high school, concentrate on your studies and club activities.
Geez... I get it, Papa.
高嶺
Hey, how do you put backspin into your serve?
I can't do that!
Why? Rina-senpai said there was a person who was doing it.
Rina-senpai is first ranked in the district... Doesn't she know about serve and backspin?
Do you know how do you do it?
If it's an over-serve you can't do a backspin. For that you have to put strength below and hit.
Isn't that a slice?
It's not a slice serve. You do it at this angle... this way...
Without a racket, I can't possibly know how.
That's why it's like this easy to do it like this. Like this!
Are you feeling okay?
Nevermind.
高嶺
Sometimes my backhand and top spin don't come right...
Oh, then it's non-spining. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, you have a lot of two-handed hits, right?
I'm better at using both hands because I hit it by just rotating my body.
If you lower your racket's head when you hit it back, you'll naturally get a topspin.
It's easier said than done.
It's like this... All you have to do is take it back and return it like this.
I don't have my racket, so I can't make head nor tails of this.
Look at my wrist, pull out like this... Like this!
Are you okay?
I just slipped a little.
Fufu, don't overdo it okay?
高嶺
...What's wrong?
No, it's nothing.
...I see.
You are watching me, aren't you?
Can't you tell?
I don't hate, but...
Then it's not troublesome, right?
Huh?
高嶺
You're watching me again.
Fufu, I wanted to see you.
Why? I don't think I'm fun to watch.
No, it's fun, don't you think?
... I don't have fun looking at myself at the mirror.
Do you think that might be a problem?.
No, but it might be fun to see your face, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...I don't have fun looking at myself at the mirror either, you know?
I don't think that’s the prob... What?
Fufu, now we're having fun, right?
（Well, this is funny）
